<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>O mnie — Aurelia Iwanow</title>
<style>
  :root{
    --bg: #0b0a09;
    --bg-soft: #121110;
    --gold: #d39a3c;
    --gold-light: #e8b860;
    --text: #f3f1ec;
    --text-dim: #b9b5ad;
    --line: rgba(243,241,236,0.12);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }

  body{
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  img{ max-width:100%; display:block; }

  .wrap{ max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }

  /* ============ HERO: O MNIE ============ */
  .hero{
    padding: 90px 0 70px;
  }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.05fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .hero-title{
    font-size: 6.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }
  .hero-title .dot{ color: var(--gold); }

  .rule{
    width: 70px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 32px 0 28px;
  }

  .hero-sub{
    font-size: 1.65rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: 26px;
  }
  .hero-sub .accent{ color: var(--gold-light); }

  .hero-text{
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 420px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-photo{
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-photo img{
    width: 100%;
    height: 560px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ============ FEATURE ICONS ROW ============ */
  .features{
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .features .wrap{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }
  .feature{
    text-align:center;
    padding: 48px 20px;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .feature:first-child{ border-left: none; }
  .feature .icon{
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .feature p{
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ============ PODCAST SECTION ============ */
  .podcast{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 560px;
  }
  .podcast-image{
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .podcast-image img{
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
  }
  .podcast-content{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:center;
    padding: 60px 80px;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .podcast-content h2{
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .podcast-content p{
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    max-width: 420px;
  }
  .btn-outline{
    margin-top: 20px;
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-decoration:none;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover{
    background: var(--gold);
    color: #0b0a09;
  }

  /* ============ QUOTE SECTION ============ */
  .quote-section{
    padding: 90px 0;
    text-align:center;
  }
  .quote-section .wrap{ max-width: 820px; }
  .quote-mark{
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    line-height: 0.5;
    display:block;
  }
  .quote-mark.right{
    text-align:right;
  }
  .quote-text{
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .quote-text .highlight{
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ============ RESPONSIVE ============ */
  @media (max-width: 900px){
    .hero-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-title{ font-size: 4rem; }
    .features .wrap{ grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
    .feature:nth-child(3){ border-left:none; }
    .podcast{ grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .podcast-content{ padding: 50px 30px; }
    .wrap{ padding: 0 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ====== TU WSTAW SWÓJ GOTOWY NAV (komponent z logo, menu, przyciskiem SUBSKRYBUJ) ====== -->

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">O mnie<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
      <div class="rule"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub">Szukam sposobów,<br>by żyć <span class="accent">lepiej, dłużej</span> i <span class="accent">pełniej</span>.</p>
      <p class="hero-text">Biohacking to dla mnie narzędzia do optymalizacji energii, ciała, umysłu i świadomości — w oparciu o naukę, technologię i własne doświadczenie.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x900/1a1816/d39a3c?text=Zdj%C4%99cie" alt="Aurelia Iwanow">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FEATURE ICONS ============ -->
<section class="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="icon">🧬</div>
      <p>Dietetyk kliniczny</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="icon">🧬</div>
      <p>Studentka nutrigenomiki</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="icon">🧠</div>
      <p>Entuzjastka psychologii</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="icon">⛰️</div>
      <p>Miłośniczka nart</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ PODCAST ============ -->
<section class="podcast">
  <div class="podcast-image">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x900/2a2a2a/ffffff?text=Narciarz" alt="Narciarz w górach">
  </div>
  <div class="podcast-content">
    <span class="eyebrow">PODCAST</span>
    <h2>Biohacking<br>w praktyce.</h2>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p>Analizuję najnowsze odkrycia nauki i biohackingu, by dać Ci konkretne narzędzia do optymalizacji ciała, umysłu i świadomości.</p>
    <p>Bez mitów. Bez zbędnego szumu.<br>Tylko to, co naprawdę działa.</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn-outline">▶ POSŁUCHAJ PODCASTU</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ QUOTE ============ -->
<section class="quote-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="quote-mark">“</span>
    <p class="quote-text">
      Pełnia życia wymaga paliwa: energii, sprawnego ciała, szybkiej regeneracji i jasności umysłu.<br>
      Ale najważniejsze jest wiedzieć, kim jesteśmy i dokąd zmierzamy.<br>
      Bo o to chodzi, żeby na końcu swojej drogi móc powiedzieć:<br>
      <span class="highlight">Wycisnęłam to życie. Mogę iść. Bye!</span>
    </p>
    <span class="quote-mark right">”</span>
  </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
